            “We were doing everything we should have been doing.”
          </div>

          <p class="statement">
            At Fujifilm, employees were ignoring the newsletters and posters that were the entryway into the programs that Fujifilm invested in.
          </p>

          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-invert" href="https://www.benefitnews.com/news/how-fujifilm-uses-gamification-to-communicate-benefits" target="_blank">
            Learn More
